00:04:04.240 --> 00:04:08.810
because our trunk has to stay upright as you
see me fighting here to keep myself upright,

00:04:08.810 --> 00:04:12.010
that's what's going to make the core work
overtime.

00:04:12.010 --> 00:04:14.880
Moving on to the biceps.

00:04:14.880 --> 00:04:17.010
Our Incline Variable Curls.

00:04:17.010 --> 00:04:21.549
Now, look at me do here what looks like a
regular Incline Dumbbell Curl.

00:04:21.549 --> 00:04:22.549
