00:04:22.549 --> 00:04:23.549
What's that?

00:04:23.549 --> 00:04:28.920
As I come up, I actually am changing the angle
of where peak contraction occurs, right?

00:04:28.920 --> 00:04:36.680
In an Incline Curl, peak contraction occurs
down here in the 45 degree range of motion.

00:04:36.680 --> 00:04:42.000
However, as I sit up, not only am I shifting
that focus to the end range a little bit more

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:43.889
to get a little bit more peak contraction.

00:04:43.889 --> 00:04:47.100
But, as you can see, the abs are working as
well.

00:04:47.100 --> 00:04:53.970
